arts.ttl: Ivan Juric asks Kamaldeen Sulemana to help Southampton avoid Premier League drop
arts.sum: Forward Sulemana ended a 37-game drought stretching back more than 19 months with a goal against Swansea.

arts.ttl: Sulemana scores overdue goal as Southampton beat Swansea in FA Cup
arts.sum: Kamaldeen Sulemana ended a 37-game goal drought and Tyler Dibling scored twice as Southampton registered a first win under manager Ivan Juric by beating Swansea 3-0 in the FA Cup third round.

arts.ttl: Dibling scores twice as Southampton ease past Swansea

arts.ttl: Kamaldeen Sulemana scores overdue goal as Southampton see off Swansea in FA Cup
